@host = http://localhost:5086

### Runtime readiness
GET {{host}}/health/ready

### Elected providers, capabilities, guarantees, and corrections
GET {{host}}/.well-known/Koan/facts

### Local studio totals
GET {{host}}/api/photos/stats

### First page of the photo library
POST {{host}}/api/photosets/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "definition": {
    "context": "all-photos",
    "sortBy": "capturedAt",
    "sortOrder": "desc"
  },
  "startIndex": 0,
  "count": 50
}
